// Import statements
import React from 'react'; // Import React
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom/client'; // Import ReactDOM to render the app
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Routes, Route } from 'react-router-dom'; // Import React Router components
import './index.css'; // Import global styles if needed

// Import all your components
import MainPage from './MainPage'; // Ensure MainPage is correctly imported
import NursePage from './NursePage'; // Import NursePage component
import SurveillanceForm from './SurveillanceForm'; // Import SurveillanceForm component
import JuniorDoctor from './JuniorDoctor'; // Import JuniorDoctor component
import SeniorDoctorPage from './SeniorDoctorPage'; // Import SeniorDoctorPage component

// Create root to render React app
const root = ReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById('root')); // Ensure this line is present

root.render(
  <React.StrictMode>
    <Router>
      <Routes>
        <Route path="/" element={<MainPage />} />
        <Route path="/nurse" element={<NursePage />} />
        <Route path="/surveillanceform" element={<SurveillanceForm />} />
        <Route path="/junior-doctor" element={<JuniorDoctor />} />
        <Route path="/senior-doctor" element={<SeniorDoctorPage />} />
      </Routes>
    </Router>
  </React.StrictMode>
);
